><meta name=\"googlebot\" content=\"index, follow, max-video-preview:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-snippet:-1\"/><meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\"/><meta name=\"google-site-verification\" content=\"your-google-verification-code\"/><meta name=\"mobile-web-app-capable\" content=\"yes\"/><meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-title\" content=\"Wookporium\"/><meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style\" content=\"default\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Behind the Stitches: Our Story | The Wookporium\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Meet Marina, the creator behind The Wookporium. Learn about our passion for premium, slow-fashioned festival clothing, natural jewelry, and the music community.\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/7iiji3rf/production/71c1343569f1beccc4b869e9fa8e96aa5279c0af-3456x5184.jpg\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Behind the Stitches: Our Story | The Wookporium\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Meet Marina, the creator behind The Wookporium. Learn about our passion for premium, slow-fashioned festival clothing, natural jewelry, and the music community.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/7iiji3rf/production/71c1343569f1beccc4b869e9fa8e96aa5279c0af-3456x5184.jpg\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/icons/icon-192x192.png\" sizes=\"192x192\" type=\"image/png\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/icons/icon-512x512.png\" sizes=\"512x512\" type=\"image/png\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/icons/icon-152x152.png\" sizes=\"152x152\" type=\"image/png\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/icons/icon-192x192.png\" sizes=\"192x192\" type=\"image/png\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.snipcart.com/themes/v3.4.1/default/snipcart.css\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-screen bg-deep-bg text-warm-white antialiased selection:bg-secondary selection:text-white\"><header class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 glass-light glass-shadow transition-all duration-300 \"><nav class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\" aria-label=\"Main navigation\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between h-16\"><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 focus-visible-ring rounded-lg\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-header font-bold text-primary\">Wookporium</span></a><div class=\"hidden lg:flex lg:items-center lg:space-x-8\"><a class=\"\n                  text-lg font-semibold transition-colors duration-200\n                  focus-visible-ring rounded-lg px-3 py-2\n                  text-dark-brown hover:text-primary\n                \" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"\n                  text-lg font-semibold transition-colors duration-200\n                  focus-visible-ring rounded-lg px-3 py-2\n                  text-dark-brown hover:text-primary\n                \" href=\"/collections\">Collections</a><a class=\"\n                  text-lg font-semibold transition-colors duration-200\n                  focus-visible-ring rounded-lg px-3 py-2\n                  text-primary\n                \" href=\"/about\">About</a><div class=\"relative\"><button class=\"\n                  text-lg font-semibold transition-colors duration-200\n                  focus-visible-ring rounded-lg px-3 py-2 flex items-center gap-1\n                  text-dark-brown hover:text-primary\n                \" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-haspopup=\"true\">Shop<svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"></path></svg></button></div><button class=\"btn-primary relative min-w-[44px] min-h-[44px] flex items-center gap-2\" aria-label=\"Shopping cart with 0 items\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z\"></path></svg><span class=\"hidden sm:inline\">Cart</span></button></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 lg:hidden\"><button class=\"relative p-2 text-primary hover:bg-cream rounded-lg transition-colors min-w-[44px] min-h-[44px]\" aria-label=\"Shopping cart with 0 items\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"p-2 text-dark-brown hover:bg-cream rounded-lg transition-colors min-w-[44px] min-h-[44px]\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-menu\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></nav></header><main class=\"flex-grow\"><!--$--><main class=\"min-h-screen\"><div class=\"relative w-full min-h-[50vh] md:min-h-[60vh] parallax-bg flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden\" style=\"background-image:url(https://cdn.sanity.io/images/7iiji3rf/production/71c1343569f1beccc4b869e9fa8e96aa5279c0af-3456x5184.jpg)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black\" style=\"opacity:0.4\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-serif drop-shadow-xl\">About Wookporium</h1><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 mb-8 drop-shadow-md font-light\">Handcrafted festival fashion made with love</p></div></div></div><section class=\"py-16 md:py-24 bg-warm-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center\"><div class=\"order-2 md:order-1\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-accent-dark mb-6 font-serif\">Our Story</h2><div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-lg text-cream leading-relaxed\"><p class=\"mb-4 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg\">The Wookporium started exactly where you’d expect: in the middle of the crowd, surrounded by bass, incredible energy, and the best-dressed people on the planet.<br/><br/>Driven by a love for festival culture and a deep obsession with creating things by hand, Marina started making pieces that capture that exact high-alpine, main-stage magic. Every single item, from our hand-crocheted clothing to our natural jewelry, is dreamed up and crafted to bring a little extra joy, confidence, and color to your next show.<br/><br/>We believe in good vibes, unforgettable sets, keeping your festival wardrobe premium, and, honestly? Keeping Marina’s horses fed. Because every piece you take home doesn&#x27;t just get you hooked up with a gorgeous new look, it funds a lifelong equestrian passion, too.<br/><br/>Made by hand. Worn in the crowd. Built for the beautiful people who make the scene what it is.</p></div><div class=\"mt-8 \"><div class=\"font-accent text-3xl md:text-4xl text-terracotta transform -rotate-2 origin-bottom-left mb-2\">Marina</div><div class=\"text-secondary text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold ml-1\">Founder &amp; Curator</div></div></div><div class=\"order-1 md:order-2\"><div class=\"relative aspect-square rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl\"><img alt=\"Our Story\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 50vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2F1dce159e6531a2ca37072839f65d85a72f9b5258-2486x2590.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2F1dce159e6531a2ca37072839f65d85a72f9b5258-2486x2590.jpg&amp;w=375&amp;q=75 375w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2F1dce159e6531a2ca37072839f65d85a72f9b5258-2486x2590.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2F1dce159e6531a2ca37072839f65d85a72f9b5258-2486x2590.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2F1dce159e6531a2ca37072839f65d85a72f9b5258-2486x2590.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2F1dce159e6531a2ca37072839f65d85a72f9b5258-2486x2590.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2F1dce159e6531a2ca37072839f65d85a72f9b5258-2486x2590.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2F1dce159e6531a2ca37072839f65d85a72f9b5258-2486x2590.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2F1dce159e6531a2ca37072839f65d85a72f9b5258-2486x2590.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2F1dce159e6531a2ca37072839f65d85a72f9b5258-2486x2590.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 md:py-24 bg-primary/5\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-accent-dark text-center mb-12 font-serif\">What We Believe</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-md shadow-lg border border-white/40 rounded-xl p-8 hover:transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-accent-dark mb-3\">Made for the Music</h3><p class=\"text-cream leading-relaxed\">We believe festival fashion should be as unforgettable as the sets you catch. Every piece is built to stand out, dance comfortably, and handle the energy of the crowd.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-md shadow-lg border border-white/40 rounded-xl p-8 hover:transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-accent-dark mb-3\">Slow, Intentional Fashion</h3><p class=\"text-cream leading-relaxed\">No mass factories here. We reject fast fashion by keeping production entirely in-house. When you wear our apparel, you&#x27;re wearing an authentic, premium piece made step-by-step by real hands.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-md shadow-lg border border-white/40 rounded-xl p-8 hover:transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-accent-dark mb-3\">Spreading Real Joy</h3><p class=\"text-cream leading-relaxed\">The absolute best part of this side business is getting people hooked up with cute apparel they genuinely love. We create to bring extra color, confidence, and smiles to the beautiful people in our community.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 md:py-24 bg-warm-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-accent-dark text-center mb-12 font-serif\">How We Create</h2><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12\"><p class=\"text-lg text-cream leading-relaxed text-center\">Every design at The Wookporium begins with inspiration pulled directly from the festival grounds—the vibrant lights, the movement of the crowd, and the natural textures of high-alpine environments.\n\nMarina obsessively selects ultra-soft, premium yarns for her apparel and sources high-quality crystals and earth-grown materials for her handmade jewelry. From the very first stitch of a bucket hat to the intricate wrapping of a pendant, everything is crafted by hand during focused hours at her workspace.\n\nWhen she isn&#x27;t buried in yarn or designing new festival fits, she’s out at the stables tending to her horses. Your support doesn&#x27;t just fund independent, handmade art—it directly fuels an authentic passion for the music community and a lifelong equestrian dream. Every piece truly tells a story.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 mt-8\"><div class=\"col-span-12 md:col-span-7 relative aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl transform transition-transform hover:scale-[1.01]\"><img alt=\"In the studio crafting\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 60vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2F3c5ea45196e18f1f6fcefed099679a0155aef68b-2976x1984.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2F3c5ea45196e18f1f6fcefed099679a0155aef68b-2976x1984.jpg&amp;w=375&amp;q=75 375w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2F3c5ea45196e18f1f6fcefed099679a0155aef68b-2976x1984.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2F3c5ea45196e18f1f6fcefed099679a0155aef68b-2976x1984.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2F3c5ea45196e18f1f6fcefed099679a0155aef68b-2976x1984.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fpr